---
// Game landing page for Tune the Dial
---

<html>
  <head>
    <title>Tune the Dial | ephergent.com</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@900&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #0a0a1a 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      .game-hero {
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        color: #0ff1ce;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .tagline {
        color: #0ff1ce;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff1ce44;
      }
      .nav-link {
        color: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #0ff1ce;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .nav-link:hover {
        background: #0ff1ce;
        color: #0a0a1a;
      }
      .game-card {
        background: rgba(10,16,32,0.8);
        border: 1px solid #0ff1ce33;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .frequency-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }
      .freq-item {
        background: rgba(15,241,206,0.08);
        border: 1px solid #0ff1ce33;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      .specs {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .spec-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0ff1ce22;
      }
      .spec-label {
        color: #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .scanlines {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
        pointer-events: none;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          transparent, transparent 6px,
          #0ff1ce08 7px, transparent 8px
        );
        z-index: 10;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden p-8">
    <div class="scanlines"></div>
    <div class="game-card">
      <h1 class="game-hero text-4xl font-black mb-2 text-center">TUNE THE DIAL</h1>
      <p class="tagline text-center mb-8">Turn the dial. Find the signal. Hear what the universe is saying.</p>

      <div class="specs">
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Genre</span><span>Frequency Puzzle</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Engine</span><span>Godot 4</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Size</span><span>11.2 MB</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Season</span><span>1</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Character</span><span>Pixel Paradox</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Price</span><span>Free forever</span></div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#0ff1ce88] mb-2">The Five Frequencies</p>
        <div class="frequency-list">
          <div class="freq-item">Prime Material</div>
          <div class="freq-item">Nocturne Aeturnus</div>
          <div class="freq-item">Cogsworth Cogitarium</div>
          <div class="freq-item">Verdantia</div>
          <div class="freq-item">The Edge</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        Pixel Paradox built the first prototype in a DRM basement, during a lunch break she wasn't supposed to take, from parts she requisitioned under a project code that didn't exist. She called it a hobby project. The DRM called it evidence. The DRM was right to be concerned. The device worked.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        What Pixel didn't know: the DRM basement was built on a thin spot. The device didn't receive radio signals. It received signals from other realities bleeding through the walls. A window into the Space between worlds — built by accident, by a data analyst who just wanted to understand the weird readings in her spreadsheet.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a href="/games/tune-the-dial/play/" class="nav-link font-bold">Play Now</a>
        <a href="/games/tune-the-dial/about/" class="nav-link">About</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
